original: Zielfelt, Einar, statens lantbruksingenjör, Växjö, f. 14/8/98 i Kullerstad, Östergötl. 1., av kapt. Hj. Z. o. Fred-rique v. Boisman. G. 1. 29 m. Ingrid Nordberg; 2. 35 m. Ingegerd Wilner, Barn: Ann-Charlotte f. 31, Monica 32, Lars 37, Karin 42. — Stud:ex. i Norrköp. 18, stud. v. KTH 18-21, v. Alnarps lantbr:inst. 21-22. E. lantbr:ing. i Västerb. 1. 28, tf. lantbr:ing. i Östergötl. 1. 31-33, i Kronob. 1. 33, statens lantbr:ing. i Växjö fr. 33.
translated: Zielfelt, Einar, State Agricultural Engineer, Växjö, b. 14/8/98 in Kullerstad, Östergötland. Son of Captain Hj. Z. and Fredrique v. Boisman. Married 1st in 1929 to Ingrid Nordberg; married 2nd in 1935 to Ingegerd Wilner. Children: Ann-Charlotte, b. 1931, Monica, b. 1932, Lars, b. 1937, Karin, b. 1942. Completed secondary school in Norrköping in 1918, studied at the Royal Institute of Technology from 1918-1921, and at Alnarp Agricultural Institute from 1921-1922. Employed as an Agricultural Engineer in Västerbotten from 1928, acting Agricultural Engineer in Östergötland from 1931-1933, in Kronoberg from 1933, and State Agricultural Engineer in Växjö since 1933.
